00:28:01.796 --> 00:28:06.234 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
The love that they showed to us
—it was just astounding.

00:28:06.234 --> 00:28:08.336 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
It was just so amazing.

00:28:08.336 --> 00:28:12.574 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And that’s what helped us to get through,

00:28:12.574 --> 00:28:14.743 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
to get through it all

00:28:14.743 --> 00:28:18.446 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
—it was our family, our spiritual family.

00:28:25.854 --> 00:28:29.324 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
The City of Virginia Beach, they volunteered

00:28:29.324 --> 00:28:32.961 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
