of the victims’ arrangements.

00:28:36.064 --> 00:28:38.166 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Because of the amount of people,

00:28:38.867 --> 00:28:41.503 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
the venue that they decided upon

00:28:42.237 --> 00:28:44.472 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
was the opera house in Norfolk.

00:28:45.407 --> 00:28:48.877 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
The brothers, they got everything together.

00:28:48.877 --> 00:28:53.181 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
The city didn’t really have to do anything;
they just gave us the venue.

00:28:53.181 --> 00:28:55.550 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And what really impressed them,

00:28:55.550 --> 00:28:58.553 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
the city, was that

00:28:58.553 --> 00:29:03.057 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
the whole memorial, everything,

00:29:03.057 --> 00:29:05.627 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
took place within an hour.

00:29:05.627 --> 00:29:08.096 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
The city officials were there in attendance.

00:29:08.096 --> 00:29:10.498 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
You had the local newspapers

00:29:10.498 --> 00:29:13.168 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
who covered it, reporters.

00:29:13.168 --> 00:29:15.203 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
The reporters

00:29:15.203 --> 00:29:19.107 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
were persistent in wanting to talk,

00:29:19.107 --> 00:29:23.077 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and so actually two of my brothers,

00:29:23.077 --> 00:29:25.246 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
they handled all of that information,

00:29:25.246 --> 00:29:29.350 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
with the guidance
from those two brothers who came down.

00:29:29.350 --> 00:29:33.755 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
It kept us from having
to even worry about that, you know, 

00:29:33.755 --> 00:29:36.524 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
so it was very helpful.

00:29:36.524 --> 00:29:38.760 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I continue to get cards;

00:29:38.760 --> 00:29:42.163 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I get texts from people,

00:29:42.163 --> 00:29:46.768 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and it just encourages me.

00:29:46.768 --> 00:29:50.038 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Isaiah 41:10

00:29:50.038 --> 00:29:52.073 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
—that has become my favorite scripture.

00:29:53.875 --> 00:29:55.877 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“I will really hold on to you

00:29:55.877 --> 00:29:58.913 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
with my right hand of righteousness.”

00:29:59.314 --> 00:30:01.316 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Going through this,

00:30:01.316 --> 00:30:03.852 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I could really feel Jehovah’s hand.

00:30:04.953 --> 00:30:09.924 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
It’s as if he was rubbing my shoulders

00:30:09.924 --> 00:30:13.895 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and saying: ‘It’s going to be all right.

00:30:13.895 --> 00:30:15.096 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
‘You’ll be all right.

00:30:15.096 --> 00:30:17.732 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I’m going to get you through this.’

00:30:17.732 --> 00:30:19.767 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And he has.

00:30:21.369 --> 00:30:24.405 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Each day he gets me through this.

00:30:24.405 --> 00:30:28.076 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
If it can happen to someone else,
it can happen to me.

00:30:28.076 --> 00:30:30.645 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And in this instance, it did.

00:30:30.645 --> 00:30:32.680 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
But

00:30:32.680 --> 00:30:36.985 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
that helps me to keep a perspective,

00:30:36.985 --> 00:30:40.188 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and I reflect on how Jehovah

00:30:40.188 --> 00:30:42.991 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
is going to reverse it.

00:30:42.991 --> 00:30:46.227 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
That’s my biggest hope

00:30:46.227 --> 00:30:49.664 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
—to see Jehovah reverse

00:30:49.664 --> 00:30:51.933 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
the damage that has been done.

00:30:51.933 --> 00:30:55.203 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
He’s promised it, and my faith

00:30:55.203 --> 00:30:58.706 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
is in the fulfillment of his promises.

00:30:58.706 --> 00:31:03.678 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
So I look forward to being reunited
with my daughter.

00:31:05.914 --> 00:31:09.517 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Isaiah 43:2 says, in part:

00:31:09.517 --> 00:31:13.688 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“When you pass through the waters,
I will be with you,

00:31:13.688 --> 00:31:17.692 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and through the rivers,
they will not flood over you.”

00:31:19.260 --> 00:31:21.663 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Tragic and unforeseen things

00:31:21.663 --> 00:31:24.832 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
can befall faithful servants of Jehovah.

00:31:24.832 --> 00:31:29.837 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We may suffer terribly,
but we are not destroyed.

00:31:29.837 --> 00:31:33.107 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We will always belong to Jehovah,

00:31:33.107 --> 00:31:35.410 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“the Father of tender mercies.”

00:31:35.410 --> 00:31:38.479 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Jehovah is always there for us,

00:31:38.479 --> 00:31:41.516 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
but we all lead such busy lives.

00:31:41.516 --> 00:31:45.853 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Our new music video vividly shows
the blessings we receive

00:31:45.853 --> 00:31:48.556 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
